OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome
OL,6,Fbrightness in the east this evening.
OL,7,FOtherwise rather cloudy with patchy
OL,8,Flight rain in the west. The east will
OL,9,Fremain largely dry. Freshening
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds in the northwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FPatchy rain at first.
OL,13,FOtherwise dry and rather cloudy, some
OL,14,Fhazy sunshine developing in the east
OL,15,Fduring the afternoon. Further rain
OL,16,Fspreading east in the evening. Breezy
OL,17,Fin the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
