OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fspreading southeast on Saturday
OL,7,Fmorning, although light and patchy in
OL,8,Fthe east, then brighter with a few
OL,9,Fshowers. Bright spells and showers
OL,10,FSunday. Dry start Monday, then rain
OL,11,Flater.
